# Support Scope

## Supported Versions

| Version | Status | End of Support |
|---------|--------|----------------|
| latest  | Active | N/A            |

## Support Duration

- **Active support**: Bug fixes and security patches for the latest release
- **Security-only**: Critical security patches only for previous releases
- **End of life**: No further updates

## What Is Supported

- Bug reports for supported versions
- Security vulnerability reports (see [SECURITY.md](SECURITY.md))
- Feature requests via GitHub Issues

## What Is Not Supported

- Custom deployments or forks
- Versions that have reached end of life